       WorkTypeDef defNames (confirmed from WorkTypeDefOf):
         Mining, Crafting, Cooking, Doctor, Construction, Hunting,
         Handling, Research, Growing, PlantCutting, Smithing
       Art jobs run under Crafting in vanilla.
       HediffDef names (confirmed from Hediffs_Local_Injuries.xml):
         Bruise, Cut, Scratch, Burn, Misc, Stab, Crack, Crush
       Severity guide: 0.03 = very minor, 0.05 = minor, 0.08 = noticeable
  ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->

